moe - minimal open editor
=========================
moe is an extremely fast and small text editor for Linux and UNIX systems


Requirements
------------
None for now.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (moe is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default.)

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install moe (if
necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running moe
------------
Run moe via any terminal.

control + q to quit.
control + s to save
